### ==========================================
###          TOUR REVIEWS
### ==========================================

### Get All Tour Reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/tours/reviews

###

### Get Reviews By Tour ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/tours/reviews/{{tourId}}

###

### Create Tour Review
POST {{baseUrl}}/tours/reviews/create
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "tour_id": "{{tourId}}",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Tour rất tuyệt vời!"
}

###

### Approve Tour Review
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tours/reviews/approve/{{tourId}}

###

### Update Tour Review
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tours/reviews/update/{{tourId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "comment": "Rất tốt, sẽ quay lại!"
}

###

### Delete Tour Review
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tours/reviews/delete/{{tourId}}

